{"tid":1734543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀班家長點解唔勸下佢地嘅細路投降","createTime":"2019-11-18T11:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T12:52:28.000Z","uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6c59e342d446bea1c485ba99a680bbc90a6cc818","tid":1734543,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:00:52.000Z","msg":"如果真係想佢地安全得呢個方法<br />\n搵媒體直播入去polyu<br />\n等入面嘅人知道出面嘅屋企人好擔心佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781d7940a03936ea0b29b6570c6a893a4cfab594","tid":1734543,"uid":198590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"會員 #165028 - Frizzle(港豬) 極有可能係五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍, 請大家多加注意!<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 周街都貼連豬搞到心都煩哂</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>睇見隻豬就火滾想撕左佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 誠哥真係好醒目</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>開金口講句要對年青人網開一面<br />\n而家旗下百佳, 豐澤等避開一劫<br />\n如果唔係被暴徒燒毀打爛唔知幾多間<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" /><br />\n我而家見到黑衫蒙面阻住我架車都唔出聲屌佢地<br />\n作狀支持佢地俾個like 等佢地放行<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 想同琴晚太子站嘅一個勇武道歉</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>因為我當時太驚又怕死<br />\n所以同其他乘客撞你出門口<br />\n希望你無事<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" /><br />\n原諒我<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 好怕d勇武派</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>街上面見到佢地都會避之則吉<br />\n怕會招惹埋d警察<br />\n琴日黃大仙站成班又面罩又防具咁衝入車廂<br />\n嚇到我下個站即刻落車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - （求屌醒）一直唔明白你地搞抗爭做咩</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>我80後 本身都係中產階級 收入穩定又係專業人士<br />\n雖然近呢個月都聽左好多理據話要爭取好多野<br />\n包括撤回逃犯條例 調整警權過大 之類<br />\n但係我就唔明點解一定要搞到武力衝突先收手<br />\n再加上止舉令警民官民矛盾越來越大 對香港真係好咩<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞咁多野 真心唔明每個星期搞一兩單衝突暴動真係好咩 已經港九新界都搞砸哂<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c82d4c74546b4311c4f81c2bcfc5de5a0c124178","tid":1734543,"uid":15509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:02:15.000Z","msg":"Mark咗係鬼"},{"pid":"68aed35aafac61a4d6b8e916d23d13dac1fad1c4","tid":1734543,"uid":32683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:03:12.000Z","msg":"如果理大班學生有咩事 <br />\n家長應該去殺哂黑警d仔女"},{"pid":"3d4a23318a0ecd00b1a5ee30240d9c5ad97c8fef","tid":1734543,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n媽媽別哭"},{"pid":"8d9f4297b08577ce8f91fb8b4715125e8cb54d2d","tid":1734543,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:09:04.000Z","msg":"[長期追擊] 樓主五毛 起底 block   <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">善用不推文回覆</span></span>"},{"pid":"2cf9d5cd46e1694d0aea578a7c74d9f915c3c866","tid":1734543,"uid":336561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/n